{"tid":514184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今次脆香雞翼仲大獲過民主，我地要站出來批鬥老麥","createTime":"2017-12-30T09:55:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-09T21:00:35.000Z","uid":31887,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ed22c1e2df44d0662d93c79a98e9e6b2efb9ed43","tid":514184,"uid":31887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T09:55:17.000Z","msg":"無雞翼換我今日都返唔到工了<br />\n影響民生之事應該要站出來"},{"pid":"18cf6d4a1200f151fce72ffb3dd50e2e8176f80d","tid":514184,"uid":62226,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T09:57:04.000Z","msg":"福喜問題可以忍，但雞翼冇得揀全翼就唔可以忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42f41cea2a74f28b56b1a9bd9f6a599b36e0fc47","tid":514184,"uid":104213,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T09:58:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/30/175747_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F30%2F175747_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=853276b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今晚幫襯m記先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc18b8cac00f33f5817361e4a939137455363982","tid":514184,"uid":31887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T09:58:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>福喜問題可以忍，但雞翼冇得揀全翼就唔可以忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我準備聯同各大大學教授寫討賊檄文<br />\n行天道誅逆賊"},{"pid":"18071d5dbfb1e1eb05c7a9896b3445a0c9f5ee47","tid":514184,"uid":31887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T10:01:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/30/175747_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F30%2F175747_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=853276b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今晚幫襯m記先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n建立政權後會法律限制你食四隻全槌"},{"pid":"8fbc00afead66b7301450c7a8184f5272e592c18","tid":514184,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T10:03:06.000Z","msg":"睇下d正負評數就知連登仔幾愛大財團<br />\n平時就鬧開中共同政府<br />\n一到大財團做d 仆街野大部份連登仔即刻藍屍思維上身<br />\n<br />\n藍屍:政府聽反對聲音係人情唔聽係道理<br />\n連登仔:大財團聽顧客聲音係人情唔聽係道理"},{"pid":"804e1c0188e7beaf3859e150c1fcc629d88e4347","tid":514184,"uid":85163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T10:07:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cfff94e9ce88d66dff50280d810e3c8f1644f934","tid":514184,"uid":31887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T10:12:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得喇得喇你咪以後唔好幫襯m記，執硬笠<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係 他日推返金拱門<br />\n我會成立牡丹樓<br />\n邊個反對我<br />\n建國後會迫佢食全雞槌"},{"pid":"98b55b611e2b8f816b7372e943db6f73be335bfd","tid":514184,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T10:53:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7fe1c044ae7723bdb0a78b75621f2fe3cd43d45","tid":514184,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T11:50:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4780f5344a627f6b32514b6855cac29fe848e64","tid":514184,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T21:00:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}